<script type="math/tex">\textbf{1.}</script> Go to your github homepage and create a Personal Access Token <br />
Â  Â  Â  Â   1a. On the home page, click on the arrow in the upper right corner <br />
Â  Â  Â  Â     1b. Click on â€œSettingsâ€  <br />
